        "TileImage": "$($repository 7433853d-2251-4267-9593-1a0c15902003).Image",
        "Description": "Our client, H&#233;ctor Delgado, wrote a love letter to Andrea Mart&#237;nez, but it was stolen from his office before it could be delivered. H&#233;ctor discovered the guard who stole his flowery letter, and he has hired us to make things right. Also, eliminate the two staff members who helped cover up the theft. These three stole H&#233;ctor&#39;s chance at love, so you must sow the seeds for their destruction.\rGood Luck, 47",
